Zombies are monsters found within the entrance section of Entrana Dungeon. Previously, they were pivotal to players doing the Lost City quest, as in order to chop the Dramen tree at the end of the dungeon, they needed a hatchet, which zombies can be seen wielding and may drop. With the toolbelt update, players can chop trees without having a hatchet in their inventory. They are still unique in that they can still drop hatchets directly and not tiny bladed salvage items in their stead.
